Run "make" or "make malloc" to get 
the archive and shared objects
    -libmalloc.a
    -libmalloc.so

Run "make intel-all" to make the testing
libraries run

I hope the comments help the readability of the code because it can
seem a little much. I am consolidated my code to keep it from 
repeating so lots of helper functions were used.

My malloc file is called malloc_lib.c not malloc.c. I named 
it before looking at the instructions. whoops!